'Yan majalisar dokokin Wales na tsoron kada su zama 'yan iska
Wasu 'yan majalisa sun firgita da shawarar canza sunayensu zuwa MWP (Member of the Welsh Parliament  Memba na majalisar Wales).
Wannan shawara ta samo asali ne daga shirin canza sunan taron zuwa majalisar Wales.
'Yan majalisa daga jam'iyyun siyasa daban-daban suna tsoron cewa hakan zai jawo ba'a.
Wani dan majalisa na Labour ya ce jam'iyyarsa na damuwa da cewa aƙaƙƙen yana da lafazi tare da kalmomin twp da pwp.
Ga masu karatu a waje da Wales: a cikin Welsh twp yana nufin wawa kuma pwp yana nufin kuraje.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Welsh ya ce jam'iyyar baki daya ba ta gamsu ba kuma tana ba da shawarwari.
Wani dan majalisa na jam'iyyar Conservative ya bayyana cewa jam'iyyarsa tana neman sauya sunan liberal.
A wannan mahallin, ana furta haruffan Welsh w kamar yadda ake furta su u.
A halin yanzu, kwamitin majalisar yana aiki kan wani kudiri na dokar da za ta kawo sauye-sauyen sunaye, wanda ya ce: A bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisa da kansu ne za su dauki alhakin yanke shawara kan ko za a nada 'yan majalisa.
Dokar Gudanar da Wales ta 2017 ta ba da ikon Majalisar Wakilai ta Wales don canza sunanta.
