Game da kiran 'yan majalisa, Hukumar ta fi son sunan Members of the Welsh Parliament (WMP), amma ta sami goyon baya mafi yawa a cikin tattaunawar jama'a tare da zaɓi na MWP.
A bayyane yake cewa 'yan majalisa suna kokarin samar da wasu hanyoyin, amma cimma yarjejeniya na iya zama matsala, musamman ga shugaban majalisar Elin Jones, wacce za ta gabatar da kudurin sauye-sauyen a cikin makonni kadan.
Dokokin gyare-gyare za su kuma hada da wasu canje-canje game da yadda majalisa ke aiki, ciki har da dokokin hana 'yan majalisa shiga majalisa da kuma tsarin kwamitocin.
