Taron Trump a West Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaban kasa Donald Trump ya fara taron farko a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne taron farko da Trump ya shirya yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da wasu wuraren da za a je, kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Bayan da aka dakatar da zaben dan takararsa a kan kujerar Kotun Koli, Trump ya yi niyyar gina goyon baya ga zaben tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa, saboda 'yan Republican na fuskantar rashin iko a zaben Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne taron Trump zai gudana a West Virginia yau kuma a ina za ku iya kallon sa a yanar gizo?
Taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia, yana faruwa ne da karfe 7:00 na yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a kan layi a ƙasa, ta hanyar watsa shirye-shiryen YouTube.
Ana sa ran Trump zai yi magana kan sauraron karar da ake yi wa Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da cin zarafin mata, yayin da aka dage zaben majalisar dattijai na mako guda, yayin da ake ci gaba da binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin taron shi ne taimaka wa 'yan Republican da ke fuskantar babban zabe a watan Nuwamba su sake samun karfin gwiwa.
A cewar Reuters, taron majalisa guda biyar da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, za su mayar da hankali ne kan karfafa masu sa kai da masu goyon baya, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan rinjaye da suke da shi a majalisar dattawa da majalisar wakilai.
"Sarrafa majalisar dokoki yana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandarsa, don haka shugaban ya yi tafiye-tafiye zuwa jihohi da dama a lokacin da ya shiga lokacin zabe", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
Taron na yau da ake yi a gidan wasan Wesbanco Arena a Wheeling, zai iya jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania da kuma daukar hankalin kafofin yada labarai daga Pittsburgh, West Virginia Metro News ta ruwaito.
A ranar Asabar, Trump zai ziyarci jihar West Virginia a karo na biyu a cikin wata guda, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin 100 a 2016.
Trump yana neman goyon bayan dan takarar majalisar dattijai na Republican daga West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya ragu a cikin binciken.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don ya kara masa goyon baya a zaben", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia.
Ryder Cup 2018: Tawagar Amurka ta nuna karfin gwiwa a fafatawa da fatan samun nasara a gasar wasannin da za a yi a ranar Lahadi
Bayan wasan da aka yi a raga uku, wasannin hudu a ranar Asabar za su iya zama abin da gasar Ryder take bukata.
Ko da yake yin amfani da igiyar motsa jiki a matsayin abin wasa ne, amma 'yan wasa suna yin imani da shi, musamman a irin wannan gasa.
To, a wane gefe ne suke ganin cewa wannan iko yana yanzu?
"Sun ci gaba da maki shida, yanzu sun kai hudu, don haka za mu iya cewa muna da ƙarfin motsawa a yanzu", in ji Jordan Spieth, yayin da yake shirin ranar gasar.
