Amma kamar yadda Spieth ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin iska mai laushi a cikin rigunansu kuma suna da dalilai da yawa na fata, ciki har da godiya ga yanayin Spieth da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka yi wasa tare duk rana kuma kowannensu ya sami maki uku daga cikin hudu.
Spieth ya kasance mai ƙwazo daga farko har zuwa rami na ƙarshe, yana nuna misali ga sauran.
Yayin da ya ci gaba da zagaye, muryoyin murna sun kara daɗaɗa, yana yin rawar jiki a kan maɓallin putt, kuma wasan na huɗu ya kasance a cikin wasan, tare da shi da Thomas biyu biyu.
Ya yi bikin nasarar da ya yi a wasan da suka yi a 15, tare da irin wannan kuka, wanda ya nuna imaninsa cewa ba a rasa tawagar Amurka ba a gasar.
"Dole ne kawai ka girgiza hannayenka ka shiga cikin wasan, ka yi tunanin ka kawai", in ji Spieth.
Babu wani daga cikin 'yan wasan da ya rage.
Akwai ramuka 18 da za ku yi amfani da su don ku yi nasara.
'Yan wasan da suka ci Spieth da Thomas a kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, su ne Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood, 'yan wasan da suka fi kowanne a gasar Ryder.
Wasu ma'aurata 'yan Turai masu ban sha'awa suna da hudu daga cikin hudu kuma ba za su iya yin kuskure ba.
'Yan wasan 'yan wasa biyu ne kawai da suka yi tsalle a ranar Asabar da yamma, amma sun guje wa tsalle a ranar Asabar da safe, da yammacin Jumma'a, da kuma sauran ramuka tara a ranar Jumma'a.
Wannan zagaye da kuma yadda makamashi ke gudana tsakanin masu zanga-zanga da 'yan wasan, ya tabbatar da cewa za a ci nasara a ranar Lahadi, kuma yana da wuya a sami wani ɗan wasa da ya fi dacewa don tabbatar da yiwuwar nasarar Turai a faɗuwar rana a kan filin wasa na Le Golf National fiye da Fleetwood ko Molinari.
Zai fi kyau su yi wasa a ramin biyu a lokaci guda.
Amma magana game da darajar Turai har yanzu ba ta da kyau.
Bubba Watson da Webb Simpson sun yi gajeren gwaji da Sergio Garcia, gwarzon wasan kwallon kafa na safe, lokacin da yake wasa da Alex Noren.
