Jordan Spieth da Justin Thomas, 'yan wasa uku da suka yi nasara a gasar, sun kafa wa 'yan wasan Amurkawa maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
Sun sami nasara 2&1 akan Jón Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain a wasannin hudu kuma daga baya suka dawo don doke Poulter da Rory McIlroy 4&3 a wasannin hudu bayan sun rasa ramukan farko biyu.
Sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup, ƙungiyar ta sami nasarar cire raunin da ta samu daga maki huɗu a lokacin da ta shiga cikin wasannin mutum, kodayake Furyk's a matsayin mai tsaron gida kawai yana buƙatar daidaitawa don riƙe kyautar.
