Tauraron wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones, Kit Harington, ya yi tir da mummunan namiji
Kit Harington sananne ne saboda rawar da ya taka a matsayin Jon Snow mai ɗauke da takobi a cikin mummunan wasan kwaikwayo na HBO Game of Thrones.
Amma, ɗan wasan mai shekara 31 ya yi tir da ra'ayin nan cewa jarumi jarumi ne kuma ya ce irin waɗannan mutane suna sa yara maza su ji cewa dole ne su yi tsauri don su daraja su.
A wata hira da The Sunday Times Culture Kit, ya ce yana ganin wani abu ya ɓace kuma yana tunanin yadda za a magance matsalar cutarwa a zamanin #MeToo.
Kit, wanda ya yi aure kwanan nan da Rose Leslie, 'yar shekara 31, wadda ta yi aiki tare da shi a wasan Game of Thrones, ya ce yana ganin cewa magance wannan matsalar yana da muhimmanci sosai.
"Ni kaina ina ganin yana da matukar muhimmanci mu magance inda muka kasa a matsayin maza", in ji shi.
Me muke koya wa maza a lokacin samartaka idan matsalar ta taso kamar yadda muke gani yanzu?
Kit ya gaskata cewa talabijin na iya zama wani ɓangare na abin da ke haifar da ƙaruwa a cikin mutum mai guba don halayen mutum.
Ya ci gaba da cewa, "Abin da aka haifa da abin da aka koya?
Mene ne talabijin da kuma abin da ke faruwa a kan titi suke koya wa matasa cewa dole ne su kasance da wannan halin?
Ina ganin wannan ita ce babbar tambaya a zamaninmu, ta yaya zamu canza wannan?
Domin a bayyane yake cewa wani abu ya ɓace a cikin samari.
A cikin hira, ya kuma yarda cewa lokacin da wasan kwaikwayon ya ƙare a bazara mai zuwa, ba zai sake yin fim ba ko kuma ci gaba da Game of Thrones, saboda ya gama da fagen fama da dawakai.
Daga watan Nuwamba, Kit zai yi fim a sabon fim na Sam Shepard game da fim din True West, wanda shine labarin mai shirya fim da ɗan'uwansa, mai fashi.
A kwanan baya, ɗan wasan ya bayyana cewa haɗuwa da matarsa Rose shi ne abu mafi kyau da ya taɓa faruwa a wasan kwaikwayo na Game of Thrones.
"Ta hanyar wannan wasan kwaikwayon na sadu da matata, don haka a wata ma'ana ta ba ni iyalina na gaba da rayuwata ta gaba", in ji shi.
A cikin jerin almara na Emmy, Rose Ygritte ta buga, ƙaunataccen halin Kit, John Snow.
Ma'aurata sun yi aure a watan Yuni na 2018 a gidan Lesley Family a Scotland.
HIV/AIDS: Kasar Sin ta Rarraba Sabbin Cutar da Kashi 14 cikin 100
China ta ba da rahoton karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan 'yan kasar da ke dauke da cutar kanjamau da kanjamau.
Jami'an kiwon lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 ne ke fama da cutar a ƙasar.
A cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu sabbin mutane sama da 40,000.
Yawancin sabbin cututtukan sun kamu da jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da na baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu sassan kasar Sin ta hanyar ƙarin jini.
