Wani sabon bincike da ake yi a wani gida a ƙasar Scotland yana son ya nuna yadda jemage suke amfani da ƙasar wajen neman abinci.
Muna fatan cewa binciken zai taimaka mana mu san yadda waɗannan dabbobi suke yin abubuwa kuma mu yi amfani da shi don mu kāre su a nan gaba.
Wani bincike da masana kimiyya daga National Trust for Scotland suka yi zai yi nazari a kan barkonon daji da kuma barkonon daji da kuma barkonon daji da ke cikin gonaki a Inverewe, a yankin Wester Ross.
