Za a iya jinkirta ganawar Trump da Rosenstein, in ji fadar White House
Za a iya jinkirta wani babban taron da Donald Trump zai yi da mataimakin babban lauyan kasar Rod Rosenstein zuwa mako mai zuwa, yayin da Brett Kavanaugh ke neman kujerar kotun koli, fadar White House ta ce a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein yana kula da aikin da lauya na musamman Robert Mueller ke yi, wanda ke binciken yadda Rasha ta yi katsalandan a zaben, da alakar da ke tsakanin masu ba Trump shawara da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar da shugaban ya yi wajen hana gudanar da binciken.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauyan kasar, kuma hakan zai shafi 'yancin Mueller, Washington ta yi ta magana tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya tattauna batun amfani da waya wajen rikodin hirar da ya yi da Trump da kuma janye shugaban kasa ta hanyar Amincewa ta 25.
Rosenstein ya musanta wannan rahoton.
A ranar Litinin da ta gabata ne ya je fadar shugaban kasa, inda ya bayyana cewa zai yi murabus.
Maimakon haka, an yi alkawarin ganawa da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yana Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
