An kwashe mutane fiye da 16,000 daga birnin Pala bayan bala'in.
Ga wasu abubuwa game da birnin Palu da Donggala da ke tsibirin Sulawesi:
Palu babban birnin lardin Tsakiyar Sulawesi ne, wanda ke a ƙarshen wani ɗan ƙaramin bakin teku a yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi, tare da ƙididdigar yawan mutane 379,800 a cikin 2017.
A lokacin da girgizar ƙasa da tsunami suka auku, birnin yana bikin cika shekaru 40 da kafuwarsa.
Donggala wani yanki ne mai nisan kilomita 300 (180 miles) a gabar tekun arewa maso yammacin tsibirin Sulawesi.
A cikin shekarar 2017, an kiyasta yawan jama'ar yankin 299,200.
Kifi da noma sune tushen tattalin arzikin lardin Sulawesi ta tsakiya, musamman yankin Donggala da ke gabar teku.
Har ila yau, hakar ma'adinai na da muhimmanci a lardin, amma an fi mayar da hankali ne a Morowali, a gabar tekun Sulawesi.
Hukumar Kula da Bala'i ta ƙasar Indonesia ta ce, a cikin shekaru 100 da suka shige, an yi tsunami a biranen Palu da Donggala.
A shekara ta 1938, tsunami ya kashe mutane fiye da 200 kuma ya halaka ɗarurruwan gidaje a Donggale.
Tsunami kuma ya auku a yammacin garin Donggala a shekara ta 1996, ya kashe mutane tara.
Indonesia tana cikin yankin da ake yawan girgizar ƙasa a cikin tekun Pacific kuma ana yawan girgizar ƙasa a wurin.
Ga wasu manyan girgizar ƙasa da tsunami da aka yi a 'yan shekarun nan:
2004: A ranar 26 ga Disamba, wata babbar girgizar ƙasa da ta auku a yammacin lardin Aceh da ke arewacin Sumatra a ƙasar Indonesia ta haddasa tsunami da ya shafi ƙasashe 14 kuma ya kashe mutane 226,000 a gabar tekun Tekun Indiya, fiye da rabin su a Aceh.
2005: A ƙarshen Maris da farkon Afrilu, an yi wata babbar girgizar ƙasa a yammacin Sumatra.
Daruruwan mutane sun mutu a tsibirin Nias da ke bakin tekun Sumatra.
2006: Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 6.8 ta afkawa kudancin Java, tsibiri mafi yawan jama'a a ƙasar Indonesia, kuma hakan ya jawo tsunami da ya auku a gaɓar teku ta kudu, kuma ya kashe kusan mutane 700.
2009: An yi wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.6 kusa da birnin Padang, babban birnin lardin Sumatra ta Yamma.
Mutane fiye da 1,100 ne suka mutu.
2010: Wata girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta auku a tsibirin Mentawai, a bakin tekun Sumatra, kuma ta haddasa tsunami mai tsawon kafa 10 da ya halaka ƙauyuka da yawa kuma ya kashe mutane kusan 300.
2016: Wani mummunar girgizar kasa ta afkawa yankin Pidie Jaya da ke Aceh, ta haddasa barna da firgici, ta tunatar da mutane da bala'in girgizar kasa da tsunami da suka auku a shekara ta 2004.
Amma mutane fiye da 100 sun mutu domin gine-ginen da suka rushe.
2018: Girgizar ƙasa mai tsanani ta afkawa tsibirin Lombok da ke ƙasar Indonesia kuma ta kashe mutane fiye da 500, yawanci a arewacin tsibirin.
Girgizar ta lalata dubban gine-gine kuma ta sa dubban masu yawon buɗe ido suka makale a wurin.
An kama babban dan Sarah Palin a kan laifin cin zarafin da ake yi a gida
Track Palin, babban dan tsohon gwamnan Alaska da kuma mataimakin shugaban kasa Sarah Palin, an kama shi kuma an tuhume shi da cin zarafi.
An kama Palin, mai shekara 29, daga Wasilla, Alaska, a ranar Talata bisa zargin aikata laifin cin zarafin mata, da kuma sabawa dokar hana yin amfani da kayan aiki, a cewar rahoton 'yan sanda na Alaska da aka fitar a ranar Asabar.
Rahoton 'yan sanda ya nuna cewa, sa'ad da wata abokiyarsa ta yi ƙoƙarin kiran 'yan sanda don ta kai rahoton waɗannan laifuka, ya ƙwace wayarta.
Palin ya ci gaba da tsare shi a gidan bincike a Mat-Su kuma an tsare shi a kan takardar da ba ta da daraja ta dala 500, in ji gidan talabijin na KTUU.
Ya bayyana a gaban kotu a ranar Asabar inda ya bayyana laifinsa, a fili, kamar yadda gidan talabijin ya ruwaito.
Palin yana fuskantar laifuffuka uku na aji A, wanda ke nufin zai iya yin shekara guda a kurkuku da kuma tara dala 250,000.
An kuma tuhume shi da laifin da ake kira Class B, kuma aka saka shi a kurkuku na kwana ɗaya kuma aka ci masa tarar dala 2,000.
Wannan ba shine karo na farko da aka gabatar da tuhumar aikata laifi a kan Palin ba.
A watan Disambar 2017, an tuhume shi da laifin kai wa mahaifinsa hari, Todd Palin.
Mahaifiyarsa Sarah Palin ta kira 'yan sanda don kai rahoton wani hari.
Yanzu haka ana shari'ar ne a kotun soja a Alaska.
A watan Janairun 2016, an tuhume shi da laifin cin zarafin gida, da kutsawa cikin rahoton aikata laifukan tashin hankali a cikin gida da kuma mallakar bindiga yayin da yake cikin maye dangane da lamarin.
Abokinsa ya ce ya buge ta a fuska.
An soki Sarah Palin a shekarar 2016 bayan da ta danganta halin zaluncin danta da PTSD sakamakon aikinsa a Iraki.
Girgizar Kasa da Tsunami a Indonesia: Daruruwan Sun Mutu
Akalla mutane 384 ne suka mutu a girgizar kasa da ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi na kasar Indonesia a ranar Juma'a.
Girgizar ƙasa mai ƙarfin awo 7.5 ta haddasa tsunami kuma ta halaka dubban gidaje.
Lantarki da hanyoyin sadarwa sun lalace, kuma ana sa ran yawan mutuwar zai karu a cikin kwanaki masu zuwa.
Girgizar ta auku ne kusa da tsakiyar Sulawesi, da ke arewa maso gabashin babban birnin Indonesia, Jakarta.
Wasu bidiyoyi da ke nuna lokacin da aka yi hatsari suna yawo a shafukan sada zumunta.
Daruruwan mutane sun taru a wurin bikin bakin teku a birnin Palu sa'ad da tsunami ya auko bakin tekun.
Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya sun nemi hukuncin kisa kan wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York
Masu gabatar da kara a New York suna neman hukuncin kisa ga Sayfullah Saipov, wanda ake zargi da kai harin ta'addanci a New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin da ba a taba yankewa ba a jihar saboda aikata laifi na tarayya tun 1953.
An ce Saipov, mai shekara 30, ya yi amfani da wata motar haya ta Home Depot don kai hari a kan hanyar keke a kan hanyar West Side ta Lower Manhattan a ranar 31 ga Oktoba, inda ya buge masu tafiya da masu hawan keke a kan hanya.
A cewar sanarwar da aka bayar a kan fara shari'ar kisa a gundumar kudu ta birnin New York, idan masu gabatar da kara suna son a yanke musu hukuncin kisa, dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Saipov da gangan ya kashe mutane takwas kuma da gangan ya yi mummunan rauni.
A kan waɗannan laifuffuka biyu, an yanke hukuncin kisa bisa ga takardar shari'a.
Makonni bayan harin, wata kotun bincike ta kasa ta tuhumi Saipov da laifin aikata laifuka 22 da suka hada da laifuka takwas na kisan kai da nufin yi wa mutane barazana, wanda ake yawan amfani da shi a kotun tarayya wajen tuhumar masu aikata laifuka, da kuma laifuka biyu na lalata motoci da kuma aikata mugunta.
Harin ya bukaci "shirye-shiryen da ya dace da tunani mai kyau", in ji masu gabatar da kara, kuma sun bayyana yadda Saipov ya aikata shi a matsayin abin ƙyama, mai zalunci da kuma lalata.
"Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleaves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erlija, Hernan Ferruchi, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damiano Pagnucco rauni da kuma asarar rayukansu", in ji rahoton da aka fitar.
Biyar daga cikin wadanda aka kashe 'yan yawon bude ido ne daga Argentina.
Shekaru goma kenan da Kudancin New York ya yanke hukuncin kisa.
An yanke wa wanda ake tuhuma, Khalid Barnes, hukuncin kisa kan wasu masu safarar miyagun kwayoyi biyu, amma a watan Satumbar 2009 aka yanke masa hukuncin daurin rai da rai a gidan yari.
An yi hukuncin kisa a New York a shekara ta 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata da aka kashe bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan laifin yin magudi da leken asiri ga Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka gabata.
An kashe su biyu a kujera ta lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
Saipov, dan asalin Uzbekistan, ya nuna rashin tabbacin lamirinsa a cikin kwanaki da watanni bayan harin, a cewar takardun kotu.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya gaya wa masu binciken cewa yana jin daɗin abin da ya yi.
A cewar tuhumar, Saipov ya ce kallon bidiyon ISIS a wayarsa ne ya sa ya dauki nauyin kai harin.
'Yan sanda sun ce ya kuma nemi a saka tutar ISIS a dakin asibitin sa.
Ya ce ba shi da laifi a kan tuhumar da aka yi masa da maki 22.
David Patton, daya daga cikin lauyoyin da ke wakiltar Saipov ya ce sun yi takaicin matakin da lauyoyin suka dauka.
"Muna ganin hukuncin da aka yanke na neman hukuncin kisa maimakon a yanke hukuncin kisa da kuma zaman gidan yari ba tare da samun damar sakewa ba ya kara wa duk wanda ya shiga cikin lamarin rauni", in ji Patton.
A baya, jami'an tsaron Saip sun nemi masu gabatar da kara da kada su nemi hukuncin kisa.
Wani dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya ya ce ya kamata Nigel Farage ya jagoranci tattaunawar Brexit
A wani zanga-zanga da aka yi a taron 'yan majalisa a yau, Nigel Farage ya yi alkawarin cewa zai garkuwa da sojojin jama'a.
Tsohon shugaban jam'iyyar Independence Party na Burtaniya ya ce 'yan siyasa sun fuskanci wata matsala daga 'yan adawa da kudin Turai - lokacin da wani dan majalisa ya ba Theresa May shawarar ya jagoranci tattaunawar da EU.
Dan majalisa mai ra'ayin mazan jiya Peter Bone ya ce a watan Maris a Birmingham cewa Birtaniya za ta kasance a baya idan Mr Farage ya zama sakataren Brexit.
Amma kalubalen da Mrs May ke fuskanta wajen rage yawan masu adawa da ita ya kara da cewa 'yan adawa da ci gaba sun shiga zanga-zangar raba gardama a birnin.
Firaministan kasar na kokarin tabbatar da yarjejeniyar da ta kulla da masu goyon bayan Brexit da masu goyon bayan ci gaba da kasancewa a cikin EU.
Allies sun dage cewa za ta ci gaba da kokarin cimma yarjejeniya da Brussels duk da adawa - kuma ta tilasta wa masu shakkar Euro da ma'aikatan aiki su zabi tsakanin kayan aikinta da ka'a.
A wani taron da kungiyar Leave Means Leave ta yi, Mista Bone ya bayyana cewa yana son a kori Firaministan kasar.
Ya ba wa Mr Farage damar shiga cikin tattaunawa da Brussels.
"Idan shi ne ke kula da wannan, da mun riga mun fita", in ji shi.
Wani dan majalisa a Wellingborough ya kara da cewa: "Zan goyi bayan Brexit, amma muna bukatar mu dakatar da firaministan".
Ya nuna rashin amincewarsa da EU, ya ce: "Ba mu yi yaƙi a yaƙe-yaƙe na duniya don mu zama bayi ba.
Muna so mu kafa dokokinmu a kasarmu.
Mista Bone ya yi watsi da ra'ayin cewa ra'ayin jama'a ya canza tun bayan zaben 2016: Ra'ayin cewa Birtaniya ta canza ra'ayi kuma tana son zama ba gaskiya bane.
Mai goyon bayan Brexit Andrea Jenkyns, ita ma tana cikin gangamin, ta shaida wa manema labarai cewa: "Ina mai cewa:
Prime Minister ba ta da farin jini a tsakanin jama'a, 'yan adawa ba za su zabe ta ba, ba ta da farin jini a jam'iyyarmu da masu fafutukarmu, wadanda a zahiri suna birkice tituna don su sa mu zama na farko.
Don Allah ku bar firaministan kasar haka ku fara sauraro.
A wata sanarwa da ta yi wa May, ta kara da cewa: "Firai ministoci suna rike da mukaman su idan suka cika alkawuransu".
Farage ya ce 'yan siyasa za su fusata idan suka yi watsi da shawarar da aka yanke a zaben raba gardama na 2016.
Wannan yanzu batun amana ne tsakanin mu − mutane − da kuma siyasarmu, in ji shi.
Suna kokarin cin amanar Brexit kuma muna nan a yau don gaya musu cewa ba za mu bari su yi hakan ba.
A jawabinsa ga jama'ar da ke cikin farin ciki, ya kara da cewa: "Ina so 'yan siyasarmu, wadanda ke kan hanyar cin amanar Brexit, su ji fushinmu".
Za mu hada kai da mutanen wannan kasa da suka ba mu nasara a Brexit kuma ba za mu yi kasa a gwiwa ba har sai mun zama 'yanci, mulkin kai, da alfahari na Burtaniya.
A wannan lokacin, masu zanga-zangar sun yi tafiya a birnin Birmingham don su ci gaba da zama, kuma suka yi taro na awa biyu a tsakiyar birnin.
Masu fafutuka da dama sun yi ta nuna takardun shaida na 'yan adawa da Brexit.
Wani dan jam'iyyar Labour mai suna Lord Adonis ya yi wa 'yan Conservative ba'a kan matsalar tsaro da ake fuskanta a lokacin da aka fara taron.
"Waɗannan mutane ne ke gaya mana cewa za su iya samun tsarin bayanai da duk fasahar da ta dace don iyakar da ba ta da wata hanya da kuma cinikayya ba tare da iyaka ba a Ireland", in ji shi.
Wannan abin dariya ne.
"Babu wani abu kamar kyakkyawar Brexit", ya kara da cewa.
Warren ta shirya ta yi tunani sosai game da neman shugaban kasa.
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta ce za ta yi la'akari sosai da neman takarar shugaban kasa bayan zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
Jaridar Boston Globe ta ruwaito cewa wata 'yar Democrat daga Massachusetts ta yi magana game da makomar ta a taron majalisar dattijai a yammacin Massachusetts a ranar Asabar.
Warren, mai yawan sukar Shugaba Donald Trump, tana neman sake zaben da ya yi da dan majalisar jihar Republican Geoff Diehl, wanda ya jagoranci yakin neman zaben Trump a shekarar 2016 a Massachusetts.
An yi hasashen cewa za ta iya doke Trump a 2020.
Taron da aka yi a ranar Asabar da yamma a Holyoke shi ne na 36 da ta yi a fadar shugaban kasa tun lokacin da Trump ya hau mulki.
Wani mai magana da yawun taron ya tambaye ta ko tana son zama 'yar takarar shugaban kasa.
Warren ta amsa cewa lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington don gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma hakan na bukatar mace a kan mulki.
An kama shi a harbin Sims na jami'ar LSU
'Yan sanda a Baton Rouge, Louisiana, sun sanar a ranar Asabar cewa sun kama wani da ake zargi da harbin dan wasan kwando na LSU Wayden Sims a ranar Juma'a.
Hukumar 'yan sanda ta Baton Rouge ta sanar da kama wani mutum mai suna Dyteon Simpson, mai shekara 20, a karfe 11 na safiyar yau a wani taron manema labarai.
Sun fitar da bidiyon harbin da aka yi ranar Juma'a kuma sun nemi a taimaka musu wajen gano mutumin da aka yi a bidiyon.
An harbe Sims, mai shekara 20, kuma an kashe shi a kusa da makarantar kwana ta Southern University a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
"Wayde Sims ya sha rauni ne daga harbin bindiga a kansa kuma daga karshe ya mutu sakamakon hakan", in ji shugaban 'yan sanda Murphy J. Paul ga kafafen yada labarai a ranar Asabar ta hanyar 247sports.
Wayde ya je ya ceci abokinsa, sai Simpson ya kashe shi.
An yi wa Simpson tambayoyi kuma ya furta cewa yana wurin, yana da makami kuma ya furta cewa ya harbe Wayden Sims.
An kama Simpson ba tare da wani adawa ba kuma aka tsare shi a ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge.
Dan wasan mai kafa biyu, wanda ya taso a Baton Rouge, ya buga wasanni 32 da farawa 10 a kakar wasa ta bara yana da matsakaicin minti 17.4, maki 5.6 da 2.9 a wasa.
Lewis Hamilton ya kusa lashe gasar cin kofin duniya bayan da ya lashe gasar da Sebastian Vettel
Tun lokacin da Valtteri Bottas ya yi tseren ne a gaban Lewis Hamilton a ranar Asabar, ya bayyana cewa umarnin ƙungiyar Mercedes zai taka muhimmiyar rawa a gasar.
Daga mafi kyawun matsayin farawa, Bottas ya sami kyakkyawan farawa kuma kusan ya sa Hamilton cikin mummunan yanayi lokacin da ya kare matsayinsa a cikin farkon kusurwa biyu kuma ya kira Vettel ya kai hari ga abokin aikinsa.
Vettel ya fara shiga cikin akwatunan farko, ya bar Hamilton ya shiga cikin zirga-zirga a bayan rukuni, wanda ya kamata ya zama mahimmanci.
Mercedes ta shiga cikin filin ajiye motoci da ke kusa da shi kuma ta bi Vettel, amma Hamilton ya ci gaba bayan tsananin tsere, inda direban Ferrari ya yi watsi da ciki tare da haɗarin ya kare kansa sau uku bayan ya yi amfani da biyu.
A ranar haihuwarsa ta 21, Max Verstappen ya fara daga jere na baya kuma ya kasance na bakwai a ƙarshen zagaye na farko.
