Ƙungiyar Elite: Dundee Stars 5 da 3 Belfast Giants
Patrick Dwyer ya zira kwallaye biyu a raga a wasan Giants da Dundee hockey
Dundee Stars sun rama rashin nasarar da suka yi a gasar Elite League da Belfast Giants ranar Juma'a ta hanyar lashe wasan ramuwar gayya a ranar Asabar a Dundee da ci 5 da 3.
Giants sun samu ci biyu a kan lokaci, tare da Patrick Dwyer da Francis Beauvillier.
Mike Sullivan da Jordan Cowne sun sa 'yan wasan gida su daidaita, amma daga bisani Dwyer ya sake jagoranci Giants.
Francois Bouchard ya daidaita wa Dundee, amma daga baya Lukas Lundvald Nielsen ya ba da kwallaye biyu da suka tabbatar da nasarar su.
Wannan dai ita ce karo na uku da aka doke 'yan wasan Elite League a kakar wasa ta bana, Adam Keefe, wanda ya doke Dundee da ci 2 da 1 a Belfast a daren Juma'a.
Wannan dai shi ne karo na hudu da ake karawa a kakar wasa ta bana, inda Giants suka yi nasara a wasanni uku da suka gabata.
Dwyer ya fara wasa a minti na hudu da 3:35 na Kendall McFaul ya taimaka, kuma minti hudu bayan haka, David Rutherford ya taimaka, lokacin da Beauvillier ya ninka jagorancin.
A lokacin da ake ta buga wasan farko, Sullivan ya dawo da gidajen a cikin 13:10 kafin Matt Marquardt ya tabbatar da daidaitawar Cownie a 15:16.
Dwyer ya tabbatar da cewa Giants sun jagoranci zuwa farkon lokaci lokacin da ya zira kwallo ta biyu a ƙarshen farkon kwata.
'Yan wasan gida sun sake haɗuwa kuma Bouchard ya sake daidaitawa ta hanyar burin wasan ba tare da mai tsaron gida ba a cikin lokaci 27:37.
Cownie da Charles Corcoran sun hada kai don taimakawa Nielsen don farko a wasan don tabbatar da jagorancin Dundee a rabi na biyu kuma ya tabbatar da nasara a rabi na karshe.
Giants, da suka rasa wasanni hudu daga cikin biyar da suka buga a yanzu, za su buga wasansu na gaba a Milton Keynes ranar Juma'a.
Wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama ya mutu don ya ceci jirgin da ke ɗauke da ɗarurruwan fasinjoji daga girgizar ƙasa
An yi wa wani mai kula da zirga-zirgar jiragen sama a ƙasar Indonesia yabo a matsayin gwarzo bayan da ya mutu don ya ceci jirgin da ke ɗauke da ɗarurruwan mutane.
Mutane sama da 800 ne suka mutu, kuma da yawa daga cikinsu ba a san inda suke ba bayan wata girgizar kasa mai karfin gaske ta afkawa tsibirin Sulawesi a ranar Juma'a, ta haddasa tsunami.
Girgizar ƙasa ta ci gaba da girgiza yankin kuma mutane da yawa sun makale a cikin tarkace a birnin Palu.
Duk da cewa abokan aikinsa sun gudu don ceton rayukansu, Anthonius Gunawan Agung, dan shekara 21, ya ki barin wurinsa a cikin wani hasumiya mai girgiza kai tsaye a filin jirgin sama na Mutiara Sis Al Jufri a Pala.
Ya tsaya don tabbatar da cewa jirgin Batik Air mai lamba 6321 wanda ke kan hanya a lokacin ya tashi lafiya.
Sai ya yi tsalle daga tashar jirgin sama da ya yi zaton zai faɗi.
Daga baya ya mutu a asibiti.
Wani kakakin hukumar kula da jirgin sama a ƙasar Indonesia, Yohannes Sirait, ya ce wannan matakin ya ceci rayuka ɗarurruwa, in ji ABC News ta Australia.
Mun shirya wani jirgin sama daga Balikpapan, Kalimantan, don mu kai shi wani babban asibiti a wani birni.
Abin takaici, mun rasa shi a safiyar yau kafin jirgin ya isa Palau.
"Mun yi matukar bakin ciki da muka ji hakan", ya kara da cewa.
A halin yanzu, masana sun damu cewa adadin mutanen da suka mutu zai iya kaiwa dubbai.
