Ƙungiyar Turai ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta 2018 ta hanyar doke ƙungiyar Amurka da ƙimar 16.5 zuwa 10.5 a filin wasan golf na Le Golf National kusa da Paris, Faransa.
Yanzu, Amirka ta yi rashin nasara sau shida a jere a Turai kuma ba ta taɓa lashe gasar Ryder Cup a Turai ba tun shekara ta 1993.
Turai ta sake lashe kambin lokacin da tawagar Denmark ta Thomas Bjorn ta samu maki 14.5 da ta bukaci domin cin Amurka.
Tauraron Amurka Phil Mickelson, wanda ya kasa a yawancin wasanni, ya harba harbinsa na farko a cikin ruwa a rami na 16 na par 3 kuma ya ba da gudummawarsa ga Francesco Molinari.
Molinari dan wasan Italiya ya haskaka a duk wasanninsa, ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka buga 5-0-0 tun lokacin da aka fara gasar a 1979.
An kori dan wasan Amurka Jordan Spieth daga gasar ta Turai Thorbjorn Olesen na Denmark.
Dan wasan da yafi kowa a duniya, Dustin Johnson, ya fadi 2-1 a hannun Ian Poulter na Ingila, wanda zai iya zama gasar Ryder ta karshe.
Tsohon jarumi na gasar Ryder Cup guda takwas, Sergio Garcia na Spain, ya zama babban zakaran gasar Turai tare da yawan maki 25.5.
