Yanayin Red Mud na yanzu: Matsakaicin yana raguwa a Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
Wani rahoto da Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ta bayar ya nuna cewa adadin ruwan da ke cikin ruwa ya ragu sosai a yankin Tampa Bay.
A cewar Hukumar Florida, an samu wasu bambance-bambance a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Charlotte da Collier, wanda hakan ya nuna cewa yawan ruwan yana raguwa.
Red mud yana ratsa kusan mil 130 na bakin teku daga Pinellas ta arewa zuwa kudancin Lee County.
An gano wasu wurare da ke da nisan mil 10 daga bakin tekun a yankin Hillsborough, amma an gano wasu wurare da yawa fiye da makon da ya gabata.
An kuma ga wasu 'yan fashi a yankin Pasco.
An bayar da rahoton matsakaitan magudanan ruwa a bakin teku ko waje a yankin Pinellas a makon da ya gabata, ƙananan zuwa manyan magudanan ruwa a cikin teku a yankin Hillsborough, manyan magudanan ruwa a yankin Manatee, manyan magudanan ruwa a bakin teku ko waje a yankin Sarasota, matsakaitan magudanan ruwa a yankin Charlotte, manyan magudanan ruwa a bakin teku ko waje a yankin Lee, da ƙananan magudanan ruwa a yankin Collier.
Har ila yau, an samu ciwon huhu a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Ba a samu rahoton cutar da ke damun iska a arewa maso yammacin Florida ba a cikin mako guda.
